  <brief_title>Phase 2 Study of ADXS11-001 in Subjects With Carcinoma of the Anorectal Canal</brief_title>
  <official_title>PHASE 2 STUDY OF ADXS11-001 IN SUBJECTS WITH PERSISTENT/RECURRENT, LOCO-REGIONAL OR METASTATIC SQUAMOUS CELL CARCINOMA OF THE ANORECTAL CANAL</official_title>
