  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a single arm Phase 2 study. Stage 1 and 2 of the study are monotherapy evaluations of
      ADXS11-001 in 31 and 24 subjects, respectively with persistent/recurrent, loco-regional or
      metastatic SCCA of the anorectal canal that have received at least 1 regimen for the
      treatment of advanced disease
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
